云计算是一种运行模式，方便，快捷，按量计费，随时扩充

云计算包括公有云、私有云、混合云

Packaged SoftWare
	You manage
		Applications
		Data
		Runtime
		Middleware
		O/S
		Virtualization
		Servers
		Storage
		Networking

Infrastructure (as a Service)
	You manage
		Applications
		Data
		Runtime
		Middleware
		O/S
	Managed by vendor
		Virtualization
		Servers
		Storage
		Networking

Platform (as a Service)
	You manage
		Applications
		Data
	Managed by vendor
		Runtime
		Middleware
		O/S
		Virtualization
		Servers
		Storage
		Networking

SoftWare (as a Service)
	Managed by vendor
		Applications
		Data
		Runtime
		Middleware
		O/S
		Virtualization
		Servers
		Storage
		Networking

云计算不等于虚拟化
云计算需要使用虚拟化技术